tuned_model <- xgboost(data = xgb.DMatrix(train_dat %>%
                                              dplyr::select(all_of(adjusted_set_variables),
                                                            - response) %>%
                                              select_if(is.numeric) %>% 
                                              as.matrix(), 
                                            label = train_dat$response),
                         params = list(
                                    eta = 0.01,
                                    max_depth = 10,
                                    objective = "binary:logistic",
                                    eval_metric = "auc"),
                         
                         nrounds = 730)
